\\
\phantom{b_0 = X,}\quad b_1 = $b1,\quad b_2 = $b2,\quad b_3 = $b3,\quad \ldots
\)

$PAR

${BBOLD}(A)${EBOLD}  
Write the beginning of the real Fourier series of \(f(x)\) 
(through frequency 3):
$BR
\( f(x) = \) \{ans_rule(70)\}
$PAR

${BBOLD}(B)${EBOLD}
Give the real Fourier coefficients for the following functions:
